Hello, thank you for calling Harmony Music School. My name is Patrick Russell. May I know your name, please?

I'm Stephanie Martinez. What do you want from me?

Thank you, Stephanie. I'm here to help you with your enrollment process. Can I get your date of birth, please?

Why do you need that?! Ugh... It's February twentieth, nineteen eighty-five!

I understand it's frustrating, but we need it for your student ID creation. Could I also have your phone number?

Fine, it's five five five, zero one two three, four five six seven. But seriously, why is this necessary?

We use it to reach out if there are changes to your schedule. Sorry for the inconvenience.

This whole process is just ridiculous. Are we done here?

Yes, that's all I needed for now. Thank you for your patience, Stephanie. Have a great day!

Yeah, whatever.
